{"id": "jei1665702553041", "title": "sort", "breadcrumbs": ["Uniface Reference", "ProcScript Reference", "ProcScript: Statements", "sort"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jei1665702553041.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">sort</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous: soap   \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous: soap   \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/znh1665702582685.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next: sort/list \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next: sort/list \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kes1665702553734.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/jei1665702553041.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/jei1665702553041.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/jei1665702553041.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2528831\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2528831\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 14, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jei1665702553041.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jei1665702553041.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jei1665702553041.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jei1665702553041\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"jei1665702553041__sort_240216\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Sort the occurrences in the hitlist for the specified entity.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"jei1665702553041__topic_d77423e1_d77424e1_d77425e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jei1665702553041__p_d77426e1_d77427e1_d77428e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">sort</span>{<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/e</span>}\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var><code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">:</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">SortOptions</var>} {<span class=\"ph gold\">;</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">:</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">SortOptions</var> }}</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jei1665702553041__p_d77429e1_d77430e1_d77431e1\">Syntax of <var class=\"keyword varname\">SortOptions</var>: {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Order</var>} {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Unique</var>} {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Type</var>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"jei1665702553041__section_w2274ab1b7b5_w2275ab1b7_w2276ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jei1665702553041__p_d77432e1_d77433e1_d77434e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">sort \"ENTITY\", \"FLD2:d u ci<span class=\"ph gold\">;</span>FLD1:a\"</code>\n</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"jei1665702553041__note_sz2_kp2_zcc\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">sort/e</span> statement is\n            deprecated. <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">sort</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">sort/e</span> are synonymous.</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jei1665702553041__topic_d50932e1_d50933e1_d50934e1_d50935e1_d50936e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d278276e134\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7448e1_d7449e1_d7450e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7448e1_d7449e1_d7450e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7448e1_d7449e1_d7450e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7448e1_d7449e1_d7450e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7448e1_d7449e1_d7450e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7448e1_d7449e1_d7450e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7448e1_d7449e1_d7450e1__entry__3\">\n Entity whose occurrences are to be sorted. If omitted, the current entity is used.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7448e1_d7449e1_d7450e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FieldName</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7448e1_d7449e1_d7450e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7448e1_d7449e1_d7450e1__entry__3\">Name of the field to sort the data on. To sort\n                        using multiple fields and their sort options, specify them as Uniface list\n                        (GOLD ; separated) or as a comma-separated list. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7448e1_d7449e1_d7450e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">SortCriteria</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7448e1_d7449e1_d7450e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7448e1_d7449e1_d7450e1__entry__3\">\n One or more options that specify the sort order, uniqueness, and NLS sorting rules. They can be defined in any order, separated by spaces. All sort options are optional, but If a field is specified without sort options, the data is sorted in ascending order.\n <p class=\"p\">if no <var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var> and no <var class=\"keyword varname\">SortOptions</var> are specified, the hitlist will be completed and no sorting will be done.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jei1665702553041__topic_d50937e1_d50938e1_d50939e1_d50940e1_d50941e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d278276e227\">Options</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Sort Options</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__1\">Sort Option</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__2\">Valid Values</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__3\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Order</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__2\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">ascending</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">A</code>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">descending</code> | <span class=\"keyword option\">D</span>\n</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__3\">Sort order</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Unique</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">unique</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">U</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__3\">Keep only unique items; discard duplicates.\n                        <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"eds1665702557855.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eds1665702557855.html\" title=\"The following examples demonstrate how you can use the sort options to control sorting behavior.\">Using Sort Options</a>. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"19\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Type</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__3\">Determines how sorting is performed by\n                     specifying the locale, case sensitivity, level, or data type. If not specified,\n                     the default is <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">nlslocale</span>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__2\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">nlslocale</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">NLS</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__3\">Sort as a string using the value of\n                        <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$nlssortorder</span>. If this is not set, the value of\n                        <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$nlslocale</span> is used. If this is not set, a binary sort is\n                     performed. <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jvl1665702552585.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jvl1665702552585.html\" title=\"You can sort data in ProcScript using several ProcScript statements and functions. The default sort order is determined by the data type of the data and the values of NLS settings.\">Sorting Based on Locale</a>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__2\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">CaseSensitive</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">CS</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">classic</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__3\">Sort as a case-sensitive string, ignoring\n\t\t\t\t locale-based sorting conventions.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__2\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">CaseInsensitive</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">CI</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__3\">Sort as a case-insensitive string, using\n\t\t\t\t the 1-to-1 character matching for Unicode uppercase and lowercase rules. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">level</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__3\">Sort data as level ID\n                     (<var class=\"keyword varname\">n.n.n</var>), so that <code class=\"ph codeph\">9.2</code> is sorted before\n                        <code class=\"ph codeph\">10.1</code>. <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"eds1665702557855.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eds1665702557855.html\" title=\"The following examples demonstrate how you can use the sort options to control sorting behavior.\">Using Sort Options</a>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" colspan=\"2\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__2 jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__3\">\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"jei1665702553041__note_w2253ab1b3b1b3b9c15b1b1_w2254ab1b3b1b3b9c15b1_w2255ab1b3b1b3b9c15_w2256ab1b3b1b3b9_w2257ab1b3b1b3_w2258ab1b3b1_w2259ab1b3_w2260ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> When specifying the following sort\n      options, it is assumed the data is in a format that can be interpreted as the specified data\n      type. <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"eds1665702557855.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eds1665702557855.html#eds1665702557855__section_p55_wjx_tcc\">Example: Sorting Using Data Type</a>.</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Numeric</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__3\"> Sort data as Numeric</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Float</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__3\"> Sort data as Float</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Boolean</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__3\"> Sort data as Boolean</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Date</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__3\"> Sort data as Date</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Time</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__3\"> Sort data as Time</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" colspan=\"2\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__2 jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__3\">\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"jei1665702553041__note_w2261ab1b3b1b3b9c27b1b1_w2262ab1b3b1b3b9c27b1_w2263ab1b3b1b3b9c27_w2264ab1b3b1b3b9_w2265ab1b3b1b3_w2266ab1b3b1_w2267ab1b3_w2268ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> When specifying the following sort options, Uniface converts the data to the specified data type before sorting:</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">$number</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__3\"> Sort Data as\n                        <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$number</span><code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var><code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">$float</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__3\"> Sort Data as\n                        <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$float</span><code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var><code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">$boolean</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__3\"> Sort Data as\n                        <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$boolean</span><code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var><code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">$date</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__3\"> Sort Data as\n                        <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$date</span><code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var><code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">$time</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__3\"> Sort Data as\n                        <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$clock</span><code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var><code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">$datim</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__3\"> Sort Data as\n                        <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$datim</span><code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var><code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">$string</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7451e1_d7452e1_d7453e1__entry__3\"> Sort Data as\n                        <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$string</span><code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var><code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jei1665702553041__topic_d50947e1_d50948e1_d50949e1_d50950e1_d50951e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d278276e652\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7454e1_d7455e1_d7456e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7454e1_d7455e1_d7456e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7454e1_d7455e1_d7456e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7454e1_d7455e1_d7456e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">&gt;=0</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7454e1_d7455e1_d7456e1__entry__2\">\n The number of occurrences sorted.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7454e1_d7455e1_d7456e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;0</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7454e1_d7455e1_d7456e1__entry__2\">\n An error occurred. <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains the exact error.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7454e1_d7455e1_d7456e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-1</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7454e1_d7455e1_d7456e1__entry__2\">\n An error occurred in <var class=\"keyword varname\">SortSpecs</var>, for example, the field specified is not on the active path.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7454e1_d7455e1_d7456e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-2</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7454e1_d7455e1_d7456e1__entry__2\">\n An error occurred in <var class=\"keyword varname\">EntityName</var>, for example, the entity specified is not in the component structure and layout.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7457e1_d7458e1_d7459e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 4. </span><span class=\"title\">Values commonly returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">sort</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7457e1_d7458e1_d7459e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7457e1_d7458e1_d7459e1__entry__2\">\n Error constant\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7457e1_d7458e1_d7459e1__entry__3\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7457e1_d7458e1_d7459e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-1102</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7457e1_d7458e1_d7459e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_ENTITY&gt;</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7457e1_d7458e1_d7459e1__entry__3\">\n The entity name provided is not a valid name, the entity is not painted on the component, or there is no active entity.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7457e1_d7458e1_d7459e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-1126</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7457e1_d7458e1_d7459e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_PROPERTY&gt;</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7457e1_d7458e1_d7459e1__entry__3\">\n A property is not valid. An error occurred in <var class=\"keyword varname\">SortSpecs</var>. For example, the field specified is not on the active path.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7460e1_d7461e1_d7462e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 5. </span><span class=\"title\">Sort List Errors Commonly Returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span></span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7460e1_d7461e1_d7462e1__entry__1\"> Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7460e1_d7461e1_d7462e1__entry__2\"> Error constant </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7460e1_d7461e1_d7462e1__entry__3\"> Meaning </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7460e1_d7461e1_d7462e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"6\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-1112</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7460e1_d7461e1_d7462e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"6\">UPROCERR_OPTION</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7460e1_d7461e1_d7462e1__entry__3\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">SortOption</var>: Ascending\n                     assumed: When an option starts with an \"A\" and is not \"A\" / \"ASC\" /\n                     \"ASCENDING\".</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7460e1_d7461e1_d7462e1__entry__3\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">SortOption</var>: Descending\n                     assumed: When an option starts with an \"D\" and is not \"D\" / \"DESC\" /\n                     \"DESCENDING\".</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7460e1_d7461e1_d7462e1__entry__3\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">SortOption</var>: Unique assumed:\n                     When an option starts with an \"U\" and is not \"U\" / \"UNI\" / \"UNIQUE\".</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7460e1_d7461e1_d7462e1__entry__3\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">SortOption</var>: Invalid option:\n                     When an option can't be recognized.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7460e1_d7461e1_d7462e1__entry__3\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">SortOption</var>: Duplicate order: When an Ascending is defined over\n\t\t\t\t a Descending v.v.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7460e1_d7461e1_d7462e1__entry__3\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">SortOption</var>: Duplicate type: When a <var class=\"keyword varname\">DataType</var>\n\t\t\t\t or $<var class=\"keyword varname\">Typing</var> is defined twice.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7460e1_d7461e1_d7462e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-1101</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7460e1_d7461e1_d7462e1__entry__2\">UPROCERR_FIELD</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7460e1_d7461e1_d7462e1__entry__3\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">SortOption</var>: Field does not\n                     exist For sort \"entity\" when a fieldname is wrong or excluded. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7460e1_d7461e1_d7462e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-1129</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7460e1_d7461e1_d7462e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"2\">UPROCERR_ITEM</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7460e1_d7461e1_d7462e1__entry__3\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">SortOption</var>:\n                        <var class=\"keyword varname\">SubItemId</var> does not exist.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jei1665702553041__table_d7460e1_d7461e1_d7462e1__entry__3\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">SortOption</var>:\n                        <var class=\"keyword varname\">SubItemNr</var> does not exist. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jei1665702553041__topic_d50952e1_d50953e1_d50954e1_d50955e1_d50956e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d278276e962\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jei1665702553041__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jei1665702553041__topic_d50957e1_d50958e1_d50959e1_d50960e1_d50961e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d278276e971\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jei1665702553041__p_d77459e1_d77460e1_d77461e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">sort</span> statement sorts the occurrences in the hitlist according to the specified criteria. Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">sort</span> causes the hitlist to be completed.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jei1665702553041__p_d77462e1_d77463e1_d77464e1\">Sorting occurs along the active path starting with the specified entity. Consequently, you can sort on fields that are not contained in the specified entity, as long as these fields occur in subsequent nodes on the active path. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tci1665702553550.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tci1665702553550.html\" title=\"At any point when the structure editor is running, there is an active path which determines where processing is applied, and the order in which it occurs. It leads from the current occurrence of the outermost entity down to the current occurrence of the innermost entity.\">Trigger Activation and the Active Path in Forms</a>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jei1665702553041__p_d77465e1_d77466e1_d77467e1\">Sorting is based on the first 8K of the field data and on a maximum of 32K of accumulated field data per occurrence.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jei1665702553041__p_d77468e1_d77469e1_d77470e1\">By default, Uniface uses the data type of the specified sort field. Thus, a simple sort instruction (with no sort options), will sort a Numeric field in numerical order and a Date field according to its internal data format. When sorting String fields, the values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$nlssortorder</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$nlslocale</span> determine whether locale-based sorting rules are applied. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jvl1665702552585.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jvl1665702552585.html\" title=\"You can sort data in ProcScript using several ProcScript statements and functions. The default sort order is determined by the data type of the data and the values of NLS settings.\">Sorting Based on Locale</a>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jei1665702553041__p_d77471e1_d77472e1_d77473e1\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vkk1665702553651.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vkk1665702553651.html\" title=\"Uniface provides ProcScript instructions for sorting entity occurrences in hitlists and lists created in ProcScript. It is possible to perform multi-level sorting, enabling you to sort by several fields, each with its own sort criteria.\">Sorting Data in ProcScript</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jei1665702553041__section_upj_p1r_5bc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d278276e1026\">Example: Sorting Occurrences </h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example sorts the occurrences of the entity PERSON in\n               ascending order of family name, followed by first name:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"jei1665702553041__pre_l5f_q1r_5bc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">retrieve/e \"PERSON.ORG\"\nputitem/id vFields, \"FAMILY_NAME:a\"\nputitem/id vFields, \"FIRST_NAME:a\" \nsort \"PERSON.ORG\", vFields</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">It is also possible to sort using a comma-separated list:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"jei1665702553041__pre_m5f_q1r_5bc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">retrieve/e \"PERSON\"\nsort \"person.test\", \"FAMILY_NAME:a, FIRST_NAME:a\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jvl1665702552585.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Sorting Based on Locale</a><p>You can sort data in ProcScript using several ProcScript statements and functions. The default sort order is determined by the data type of the data and the values of NLS settings.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vkk1665702553651.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Sorting Data in ProcScript</a><p>Uniface provides ProcScript instructions for sorting entity occurrences in hitlists and lists created in ProcScript. It is possible to perform multi-level sorting, enabling you to sort by several fields, each with its own sort criteria.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mfl1718885236878.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$nlssortorder</a><p>Set or return the current sequencing rules to apply when sorting strings in entities and lists, or reading occurrences from the hitlist.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528831\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528831\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "sort Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 14, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Sort the occurrences in the hitlist for the specified entity. sort { /e } Entity , Field { : SortOptions } { ; Field { : SortOptions }} Syntax of SortOptions : { Order } { Unique } { Type } Example: sort \"ENTITY\", \"FLD2:d u ci ; FLD1:a\" Note: The sort/e statement is deprecated. sort and sort/e are synonymous. Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Entity String Entity whose occurrences are to be sorted. If omitted, the current entity is used. FieldName String Name of the field to sort the data on. To sort using multiple fields and their sort options, specify them as Uniface list (GOLD ; separated) or as a comma-separated list. SortCriteria String One or more options that specify the sort order, uniqueness, and NLS sorting rules. They can be defined in any order, separated by spaces. All sort options are optional, but If a field is specified without sort options, the data is sorted in ascending order. if no Field and no SortOptions are specified, the hitlist will be completed and no sorting will be done. Options Table 2. Sort Options Sort Option Valid Values Meaning Order ascending | A descending | D Sort order Unique unique | U Keep only unique items; discard duplicates. Using Sort Options . Type Determines how sorting is performed by specifying the locale, case sensitivity, level, or data type. If not specified, the default is nlslocale . nlslocale | NLS Sort as a string using the value of $nlssortorder . If this is not set, the value of $nlslocale is used. If this is not set, a binary sort is performed. Sorting Based on Locale . CaseSensitive | CS | classic Sort as a case-sensitive string, ignoring locale-based sorting conventions. CaseInsensitive | CI Sort as a case-insensitive string, using the 1-to-1 character matching for Unicode uppercase and lowercase rules. level Sort data as level ID ( n.n.n ), so that 9.2 is sorted before 10.1 . Using Sort Options . Note: When specifying the following sort options, it is assumed the data is in a format that can be interpreted as the specified data type. Example: Sorting Using Data Type . Numeric Sort data as Numeric Float Sort data as Float Boolean Sort data as Boolean Date Sort data as Date Time Sort data as Time Note: When specifying the following sort options, Uniface converts the data to the specified data type before sorting: $number Sort Data as $number ( String ) $float Sort Data as $float ( String ) $boolean Sort Data as $boolean ( String ) $date Sort Data as $date ( String ) $time Sort Data as $clock ( String ) $datim Sort Data as $datim ( String ) $string Sort Data as $string ( String ) Return Values Table 3. Values returned in $status Value Meaning >=0 The number of occurrences sorted. <0 An error occurred. $procerror contains the exact error. -1 An error occurred in SortSpecs , for example, the field specified is not on the active path. -2 An error occurred in EntityName , for example, the entity specified is not in the component structure and layout. Table 4. Values commonly returned by $procerror following sort Value Error constant Meaning -1102 <UPROCERR_ENTITY> The entity name provided is not a valid name, the entity is not painted on the component, or there is no active entity. -1126 <UPROCERR_PROPERTY> A property is not valid. An error occurred in SortSpecs . For example, the field specified is not on the active path. Table 5. Sort List Errors Commonly Returned in $procerror Value Error constant Meaning -1112 UPROCERR_OPTION SortOption : Ascending assumed: When an option starts with an \"A\" and is not \"A\" / \"ASC\" / \"ASCENDING\". SortOption : Descending assumed: When an option starts with an \"D\" and is not \"D\" / \"DESC\" / \"DESCENDING\". SortOption : Unique assumed: When an option starts with an \"U\" and is not \"U\" / \"UNI\" / \"UNIQUE\". SortOption : Invalid option: When an option can't be recognized. SortOption : Duplicate order: When an Ascending is defined over a Descending v.v. SortOption : Duplicate type: When a DataType or $ Typing is defined twice. -1101 UPROCERR_FIELD SortOption : Field does not exist For sort \"entity\" when a fieldname is wrong or excluded. -1129 UPROCERR_ITEM SortOption : SubItemId does not exist. SortOption : SubItemNr does not exist. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The sort statement sorts the occurrences in the hitlist according to the specified criteria. Using sort causes the hitlist to be completed. Sorting occurs along the active path starting with the specified entity. Consequently, you can sort on fields that are not contained in the specified entity, as long as these fields occur in subsequent nodes on the active path. For more information, see Trigger Activation and the Active Path in Forms . Sorting is based on the first 8K of the field data and on a maximum of 32K of accumulated field data per occurrence. By default, Uniface uses the data type of the specified sort field. Thus, a simple sort instruction (with no sort options), will sort a Numeric field in numerical order and a Date field according to its internal data format. When sorting String fields, the values of $nlssortorder and $nlslocale determine whether locale-based sorting rules are applied. For more information, see Sorting Based on Locale . For more information, see Sorting Data in ProcScript . Example: Sorting Occurrences The following example sorts the occurrences of the entity PERSON in ascending order of family name, followed by first name: retrieve/e \"PERSON.ORG\" putitem/id vFields, \"FAMILY_NAME:a\" putitem/id vFields, \"FIRST_NAME:a\" sort \"PERSON.ORG\", vFields Copy It is also possible to sort using a comma-separated list: retrieve/e \"PERSON\" sort \"person.test\", \"FAMILY_NAME:a, FIRST_NAME:a\" Copy Related Links Sorting Based on Locale You can sort data in ProcScript using several ProcScript statements and functions. The default sort order is determined by the data type of the data and the values of NLS settings. Sorting Data in ProcScript Uniface provides ProcScript instructions for sorting entity occurrences in hitlists and lists created in ProcScript. It is possible to perform multi-level sorting, enabling you to sort by several fields, each with its own sort criteria. $nlssortorder Set or return the current sequencing rules to apply when sorting strings in entities and lists, or reading occurrences from the hitlist. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}